cs.AI, cs.GT, cs.MA, cs.LG, cs.CV 

Reasoning: 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is the most likely category as the paper discusses the development of Ghost agents using a Multi-Agent Systems approach and presents sample controllers for the Ms. Pac-Man game. 
- cs.GT (Game Theory) is also likely as the paper introduces a competition and discusses the effects of Partial Observability on gameplay. 
- cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) is relevant as the paper focuses on developing Ghost agents using a Multi-Agent Systems approach. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) may be relevant as the paper discusses the development of controllers for the game. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) may be relevant as the paper introduces an updated game engine, which may involve visual elements.
